  "Description": {
    "English": "A obstacle demolition attachment for a terrestrial vehicle, compatible with the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Colossus</span> large Exocraft.<br><br>The <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Excavation Blade</span> allows the Colossus to collect a small number of resources from minerals and vegetation upon collision, and reduces grime and scratches to the Exocraft's paintwork.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种用于陆地车辆的障碍物拆除配件，可与以下部件兼容：大型<span class=\"name name-technology\">巨人</span>强化艇。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">开采刀刃</span>使巨人强化艇在碰撞时能够从矿物和植被中获取少量资源，并且还能减少强化艇表面的污垢和划痕。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種用於陸地載具的障礙物拆除配件，適用於大型的<span class=\"name name-technology\">巨人強化艇</span>。<br><br>這款<span class=\"name name-stellar\">挖掘刀刃</span>能讓巨人強化艇在碰撞時從礦物和植物中收集少量資源，並減少強化艇外漆上的汙垢和刮痕。"
  },
